name: SMALL Wasp-1 Graffiti Black Book
description:
<iframe width="350" height="197" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/vlBbKP0aw48" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

Partnering with graffiti writer Wasp-1, Paper For The People is now offering the exclusive Wasp-1 Graffiti Black Book. More than just paper, this product is designed for the heaviest of use.

50 page, wire-bound 8.5" x 5.5" book

No bleed through from markers, water color, spray paint, or airbrush

Smooth surface to minimize feathering

Will not rip or tear

100% archival quality
